### Review/Approval API Endpoints

```
GET    /reviews                          — list pending reviews (filterable)
GET    /reviews/:id                      — get review detail + entity data
PATCH  /reviews/:id/approve              — approve (sets entity status → 'active')
PATCH  /reviews/:id/reject               — reject (deletes or archives entity)
PATCH  /reviews/:id/replace              — replace with user-provided data
GET    /reviews/summary                  — counts by type/status for dashboard badge
```

#### Approve flow:
```typescript
// PATCH /reviews/:id/approve
// 1. Set pending_review.status = 'approved'
// 2. Set entity (template/room) status = 'active'
// 3. If all reviews for a WO are approved → set WO status = 'pending' (ready)
```

#### Replace flow:
```typescript
// PATCH /reviews/:id/replace  { updated_data: {...} }
// 1. Update the entity with user-provided data
// 2. Set entity status = 'active'
// 3. Set review status = 'replaced'
// 4. Re-generate work_order_tasks if template definition changed
```

---

### UI Integration Points

| Location | Feature |
|----------|--------|
| **Top nav badge** | 🔔 `3 items need review` — count from `GET /reviews/summary` |
| **Review queue page** | List all pending items with entity type, created date, trigger context |
| **Inline editing** | Click a draft template → edit sections/columns → approve |
| **Work order list** | `needs_review` status shown as amber badge, links to related reviews |
| **Room manager** | Draft rooms shown with dashed border, editable before approval |

---

### What This Gives You

| Before | After |
|--------|-------|
| Missing template → **404 hard stop** | Missing template → **draft created, WO proceeds, user reviews later** |
| Missing rooms → **silent empty WO** | Missing rooms → **smart defaults inserted, flagged for review** |
| No visibility into gaps | **Central review queue** with counts and context |
| All-or-nothing save | **Graceful degradation** — nothing blocks progress |
| No audit trail | **Full history** of what was auto-generated and who approved it |

